<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Approve Censor</title>
    <style>
        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #e2f0ff;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 35rem;
            padding: 3rem;
            margin: 0 auto ;
            text-align: center;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
        }
        .container .title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-align: inherit;
            color: #e72525;
        }
        .container .content {
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .content .note-item {
            color: #4285F4;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .content .sub-note {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .sub-note .hotline-item {
            color: #4285F4;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
        <h3 class="title">Reject of organization verification</h3>
        <p>Hi {{username}} ! Through the verification process, we regret to inform you that your auction organization's profile does not meet the requirements for verification at this time. Please review the profile information and resubmit it to us. Thank you for participating in registering your auction organization on our website.</p>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="sub-note">If you have problems, please contact the Technical Team - Hotline:
                <span class="hotline-item">0236589325</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
